FuncDef: This command specifies the SDP to be synchronized with multi-chassis peer.

ParaDef.Info: Specifies the SDP of the spoke SDPs to be synchronized with the multi-chassispeer. Values-1 to 17407.
Specifies a synchronization tag, up to 32 characters in length, to be usedwhen synchronizing with the multi-chassis peer.
Creates an entry; mandatory while creating an entry.
